Business Process Modeling

Business Process Model and Notation (BPMN) provides a graphical representation of business workflows that anyone, 
from business analyst to stakeholder, can easily understand; aiding in business process analysis and business process improvements. 
Visual Paradigm features an intuitive BPMN 2.0 modeler that lets you create professional Business Process Diagram quickly and smoothly.

